Pack your bags - you’re cordially invited to enter the RoC Atelier on @tyb.xyz. 🧳🗝️

We’ve been dreaming up a special place for our community to connect with us (and each other) on a more personal level. 💌 That’s where TYB comes in. Join the RoC community to:

➕Access sales and product drops early 
➕Flex your creativity with fun challenges
➕Earn discounts on RoC.com 
➕Connect, share tips and learn from other RoC fans

Sound interesting? Head to our bio to enter the Atelier. 🇫🇷 Plus…the first 100 qualifying members to join receive a welcome gift on us, a full-size Retinol Line Smoothing Eye Cream!

*Note: everyone is welcome to join us on TYB but coins are only redeemable in the U.S. at this time.
